'''Tarhead''' was a derogatory term for someone addicted to [[Membrosia/Legends|black membrosia]], referring to the thick consistency and dark color of the substance. During the [[Swarm War]], many of the galaxy's insectoid species became tarheads, and were used by the [[Killik/Legends|Killiks]] to attempt takeovers of their home systems.

